avalan (1.4.8-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release (1.4.8).
  * Drop pandas, playwright, RestrictedPython, youtube-transcript-api
    and tiktoken from Depends; upstream moved them out of the default
    profile into opt-in extras (browser, code, youtube) which the .deb
    does not ship.
  * Source packaging, rich, fastapi, uvicorn, aiomysql, asyncpg,
    matplotlib, sqlglot, sympy and pillow from Noble after the upstream
    constraint relaxations (no PPA rebuild required for these).
  * Relax versioned Depends to match the new upstream floors
    (pydantic >= 2.0, fastapi >= 0.101.0, uvicorn >= 0.27.0, etc.).
  * Mirror upstream's PEP 621 [project] metadata into [tool.poetry]
    via a quilt patch so Noble's poetry-core 1.9 (the only version in
    the archive) can build the wheel; the [project] table is left
    intact for pip-on-newer-hosts.
  * Add a per-binary lintian override for the missing manpages on
    /usr/bin/avalan and /usr/bin/avl (both resolve to the same Click
    help; upstream ships no man pages).

 -- Avalan Packaging Team <avalan@avalan.ai>  Tue, 19 May 2026 16:10:00 -0300

